# The error indicates that we have no iron ore left in our inventory to insert into the furnace.
# We need to gather more iron ore to continue the smelting process.

# Let's locate the nearest iron ore patch again and harvest some more iron ore.
iron_ore_position = nearest(Resource.IronOre)
move_to(iron_ore_position)

# Harvesting additional iron ore, let's aim for 10 iron ore.
harvested_iron_ore = harvest_resource(iron_ore_position, quantity=10)  # Harvest 10 iron ore.
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Check inventory after harvesting.
